messages.message: Welcome to the COS 330 module chat room! This is a place where you can ask questions and get help from your tutors and classmates. Please be respectful and keep the chat on topic. Please don't be afraid to contact me personally if you have any questions or concerns. Enjoy!
Hey thanks for the welcome! I'm really excited to get started with this module. I'm sure I'll have lots of questions for you guys. :)
Hey everyone! I'm new to this module and I'm really looking forward to it as well as looking forward to getting to know you all! I hope we can all help each other out and have a great time!
Hi. Thank you for the warm welcome. I'm really looking forward to this module. I'm sure I'll have lots of questions for you. :)
